{"tid":822534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"湯家驊後花園受襲 慘遭山竹蹂躪","createTime":"2018-09-16T11:21:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T13:04:10.000Z","uid":20058,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"75070e3633f93826ba549ff484037c006951d849","tid":822534,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T11:21:50.000Z","msg":"山竹來襲下，唔少人屋企都滲水漏水，冇爆玻璃已經好好，行會成員兼民主思路召集人湯家驊（Ronny）位於大埔康樂園大宅都遭殃，倘大嘅花園有一半樹冧咗，佢自己就喺facebook開post貼圖話好彩，「尚算幸運，只是超過花園一半樹幹斷落、屋內不時停電......」咁人冇事又的確係最重要嘅。<br />\n相片可見本來設計典雅嘅花園畀山竹吹一吹，凌亂不堪，八方問過Ronny，佢話屋企位處山谷，以往打風都「冇咁應」，所以連米字型膠紙都冇貼，誰不知今次山竹好鬼勁，「特別吹東風嗰陣最勁」，所以花園嚴重「受襲」，雖然啲樹唔係Ronny自家種，但都對咗幾十年㗎，自然都有感情㗎，禍不單行嘅係，「（連）隔離屋啲樹都斷咗，吹埋過嚟，要幫佢執埋」，唔好彩嘅係佢份家居保唔包花園位置，所以要自己掏錢維修，「希望唔會使太多（錢）啦！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180916/58688894\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180916%2F58688894&d=Ycq1ntVhL2qxiUbHFcPlBNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=be63ae0f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180916%2F58688894&h=658f78ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180916/58688894</a>"},{"pid":"6de593a7f087aaebfda21d0244bd0ac0c75d90ac","tid":822534,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T11:24:12.000Z","msg":"李福林將軍都唔保佢，就知佢幾抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e74938fb827c01ed663573eacf536f4008ba5074","tid":822534,"uid":81562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T11:57:46.000Z","msg":"睇標題以為講雪廠街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf320395a70a4981949b2ee5324907d5cabe1315","tid":822534,"uid":7421,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T11:58:39.000Z","msg":"以為講湯渣個後庭<img 